  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0da7\u0dca \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca 7\u0d9a\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba \u0d85\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0dd4\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Arjuna stops the foreign tour of 7 cricket bosses",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chairman of the National Sports Council, Member of Parliament Mr. Arjuna Ranatunga said that seven officials of the Sri Lanka Cricket Institute had planned to spend millions of rupees on an excursion to a foreign country.",
        "He emphasized that yesterday (27) while speaking to the media after visiting the Malwatu Asgiri elders in Kandy. He further said:",
        "\"Seven officials from the cricket institute had asked for permission to go on an excursion to a foreign country. They were to be paid 650 dollars per day along with business class flights and accommodation in top hotels in those countries.",
        "We, as the Sports Council, opposed it. When we stop these, we get problems. I came here to do the right thing. We will find out in the future how many unwanted people have gone abroad in this way.",
        "There is a problem with going to Dubai for the Asia Cup cricket tournament that was supposed to be held in Sri Lanka. From the side of the country and from the side of cricket, we have lost something big. If that tournament was held in this country, our turfs would be made in a way that suits us.",
        "Dubai's turf is often built to support countries like Pakistan and India.",
        "There is only a political problem in our country so far. Without that, it is not a question of exploding bombs. There should be a comprehensive investigation into our loss of the tournament.\""
      ],
